<P><H1 align=center>APPLICATION SUMMARY – CR042</H1>
<P></P>
<P>This screen shows a summary of information about the mortgage application. It 
is split into three sections; Personal Details, Business Details, and Product 
Details. This screen is only for information, and cannot be amended.</P>
<P>The personal details section displays the name, address and contact details 
of the applicants, together with the name, address and contact details of the 
applicants Legal Representatives (Solicitors).</P>
<P>The business section displays the application type (eg; New Loan), business 
type (eg; Direct), business source (application system name) and the contact 
details of the business source.</P>
<P>The product section displays the monthly premiums quoted for Buildings 
Insurance and Payment Protection, if being taken by the customer, and displays 
what stage the application is at eg; Initial Underwriting.</P>
<P>The mortgage product details are shown in the final 
box.</P>
<P>          Click OK to return 
to screen <A href="HELP_CR040.asp">CR040 – Customer Existing Business.</A></P>

